{"tid":1386029,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港法例－－關於罷工","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T09:22:18.000Z","uid":293274,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3a30230d0c12d75392816b5405f5b1b022d1e1d3","tid":1386029,"uid":293274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:34:33.000Z","msg":"第332章 《職工會條例》（２）<br />\n&ldquo;罷工&rdquo; (strike)指一群受僱用的人經共同協定而停止工作，或任何數目的受僱用的人因發生糾紛而一致拒絕、或經達成共識而拒絕繼續為某僱主工作，作為迫使他們的僱主、另一人或另一群人的僱主，或任何受僱的人或一群受僱的人，接受或不接受僱傭條款或條件 或影響僱傭的條款或條件的方法；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第57章 《僱傭條例》（９）<br />\n(2)僱主無權以僱員參加罷工而根據第(1)款終止其僱傭合約。 (由2000年第51號第2條增補)<br />\n<br />\n附表1－連續性僱傭<br />\n4. 凡僱員在任何一個小時或其部分因下列理由而缺勤 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)僱員參與不屬非法的罷工；或<br />\n(b)僱主閉廠，<br />\n則該小時不得計作為他曾經工作的小時，但其僱傭期的連續性則不會因該次缺勤而視為中斷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，即僱主可以唔出當日既糧，但唔可以因罷工炒你？有冇法律界人士可以作補充？"},{"pid":"30ffeee6c13e9ec48f5e96780202f8f78d7e419d","tid":1386029,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82c59c5168e35d123c2bf73efd047dbc5c3a3d1","tid":1386029,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"工賤會即刻開會收例罷工可以即炒囉"},{"pid":"8e98ee6ec888573c582aeeda657e1a72c2cb2cd4","tid":1386029,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f82c59c5168e35d123c2bf73efd047dbc5c3a3d1","tid":1386029,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"工賤會即刻開會收例罷工可以即炒囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"休會期有排玩"},{"pid":"41a4ca2aebcdc13152ceae1da86e686be85031f7","tid":1386029,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d0f51ce3439bea4dbc7d05933d5312a1bc384b","tid":1386029,"uid":199613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:40:05.000Z","msg":"咩係非法既罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5e9d0a29e843a13d2a679408f305de46ea5022","tid":1386029,"uid":3212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:40:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1f3d7f648e5ab1dd9ff7bd683292e8e53a1af3d","tid":1386029,"uid":279111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"推，如果罷工唔會令打工人士冇左份工，咁對我地有好大幫助"},{"pid":"d9d6cc0d606e7985b00fc4a82253fef7bc476f4b","tid":1386029,"uid":293308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:45:16.000Z","msg":"8月1號去職工盟辦公室請願，要求佢地支持8月5號總罷工。否則香港工人就應成立新工會職盟。<br />\n<br />\n8月5號罷工一定要有成功<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1381496/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1381496/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"60e37df0502dd02f6e160f9b18b31ce57226d151","tid":1386029,"uid":126226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:22:18.000Z","msg":"好似只可以係關於公司既罷工喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}